Senior, do you know how to make egg dumplings?

186
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,600
No.

187
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,000
Then what do we do?

188
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:25,600
Let whoever can do it, do it.

189
