- Can we sit here?
- Daughter-in-law, sit over here.

232
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:48,100
- Sure.
- Get Grandma some rice.

233
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,800
Thank you.

234
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:55,800
Go get Grandma some rice.

235
00:18:00,800 --> 00:18:03,600
- Let me.
- Okay.

