00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:07,000
Senior, there's a seat here.

237
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,800
Not anymore.

238
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:36,800
Brother Yuan, let's go sit over there.

239
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:40,000
Make space for Nian Nian and his wife. All right?

240
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:41,800
Get up! We will sit over there.

241
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:43,800
Let's go Brother Yuan.

242
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:48,100
Let's sit over here, okay?

243
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,300
Move their bowls over there.

244
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,800
Thank you.

245
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:14,500
